@startuml sd-01-register-issue-detailed
!include ../_shared/its-uml-style.puml

title Detailed SD 01 - Register Issue
hide footbox

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #000000
  ArrowThickness 1.4
  LifeLineBorderColor #7E57C2
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #B39DDB
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  ActorBorderColor #7E57C2
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "Auth User" as User
participant "issueController:IssueController" as IC
participant "currentProject:Project" as Project

User -> IC : registerIssue(title, description, priority)

alt not authorized
  IC --> User : permissionDenied()
else invalid title or description
  IC --> User : validationError(missingFields)
else valid and authorized
  note right of IC
  issueController는 UC1의 SSD system operation을 수신한다.
  UI, 권한 정책, 현재 사용자/프로젝트 조회,
  현재 시각, 영속성 처리는 lifeline으로 펼치지 않고
  Logical Architecture의 contextual service로 간주한다.
  end note

  IC -> Project : registerIssue(title, description, priority,\ncurrentUser, now)
  activate Project

  create "newIssue:Issue" as Issue
  Project -> Issue : createWithDefaultPriority(title, description, priority,\nstatus=NEW, reporter=currentUser,\nreportedDate=now)
  activate Issue

  Project -> Issue : recordCreation(currentUser, now)
  create "createdHistory:IssueHistory" as CreatedHistory
  Issue -> CreatedHistory : new(action=CREATED,\npreviousValue=null,\nnewValue=NEW,\nchangedBy=currentUser,\nchangedDate=now)
  Issue -> Issue : addHistory(createdHistory)

  note right of Issue
  OC-01 사후조건:
  - Issue.status = NEW
  - reporter = currentUser
  - reportedDate = now
  - priority = priority 또는 MAJOR
  - IssueHistory(CREATED) 기록
  - changedBy=currentUser는
    User-IssueHistory changes association 형성을 의미
  end note

  Issue --> Project : creationRecorded
  deactivate Issue

  Project -> Project : addIssue(newIssue)
  Project --> IC : newIssue
  deactivate Project

  note over Project
  Creator / Information Expert:
  Project.registerIssue는 Issue 생성,
  priority 기본값 적용, CREATED history 기록, contains 등록을
  하나의 원자적 도메인 작업으로 캡슐화한다.
  end note

  IC --> User : issueRegistered(issueId,\nstatus=NEW,\nconfirmation)
end

opt Auth User wants to add an initial comment
  ref over User, IC
  UC2 Add Comment
  addComment(issueId, content)
  end ref
end

@enduml
